OL,3,CLarijani's death would be a symbolic
OL,4,CUS-Israel victory but not a decisive
OL,5,Cone
OL,7,FIf confirmed, the killing of Ali
OL,8,FLarijani is another scalp for the
OL,9,FAmericans and Israel. It will be
OL,10,Ftrumpeted as a victory, and despite
OL,11,Ftheir opaque war aims, the death of
OL,12,Fanother senior leader will be counted
OL,13,Fas a win. But to overstate his value
OL,14,Fis to understate the nature of the
OL,15,FIranian system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
