OL,3,CLarijani's death would be a symbolic
OL,4,CUS-Israel victory but not a decisive
OL,5,Cone
OL,7,FOn Friday, he walked in the streets of
OL,8,FTehran to mark Al Quds Day. A few
OL,9,Fhours later, the US offered a reward
OL,10,Fof up to $10 million for information
OL,11,Fon him and other senior Iranian
OL,12,Fmilitary and intelligence officials.
OL,14,FAt the start of this war, he was seen
OL,15,Fby the Americans as a pragmatist they
OL,16,Fmight be able to do business with.
OL,17,FThat probably bought him time as they
OL,18,Fwaited for him to deliver. He did not,
OL,19,Fand today their patience ran out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
